Home ::  Men's Shoes ::  Classic Style ::  Classic Style 00005
3065 Expression #1 of ORDER BY clause is not in SELECT list, references column 'tdc07956_vgsdbg.xp.products_id' which is not in SELECT list; this is incompatible with DISTINCT
[select distinct p.products_id, p.products_image, pd.products_name from products_xsell xp, products p, products_description pd where xp.products_id = '249' and xp.xsell_id = p.products_id and p.products_id = pd.products_id and pd.language_id = '1' and p.products_status = '1' order by xp.products_id asc limit 6]
